 Slingshot Metal Darts in Chuuk: A Retrospective Review of Cases.\u201d Health Palau and Micronesia 12(1). FSM National Congress. 2005. \u201cResolution 14-6 on the National Youth Policy.\u201d http://www. fsmcongress.fm/14congress/14th congress resolutions.htm. Accessed 19 November 2010. Congress of the Federated States of Micronesia. 2010. \u201cCongressmen.\u201d http://www. fsmcongress.fm/Congressmen.htm. Accessed 16 November 2010. Government of the Federated States of Micronesia. 2004. Strategic Development Plan 2004- 2023. Volume 1: Policies and Strategies for Development. National Government. Government of the Federated States of Micronesia. 2010a. \u201cNational Government.\u201d http:// www.fsmgov.org/ngovt.html. Accessed 16 November, 2010 .2010b. National Report submitted in accordance with paragraph 15 (a) of the annex to Human Rights Council resolution 5/1. Geneva: Human Rights Council .2010c. National women\u2019s conference in Kosrae adopts gender based resolutions, FSM Information Services, Pohnpei. Press Release, August 3. HSA (Department of Health and Social Affairs). 2006. Report on the Implementation of the FSM National Youth Policy April 2005-June 2006. Pohnpei .2005. National Youth Policy 2004-2010. Pohnpei Hezel, Francis X. 1989. \u201cWhat Can We Do to Prevent Youth Suicide?\u201d Journal of the Pacific Society, Vol. 12 No. 2, July. .1997. \u201cAlcohol and Drug Use in the FSM.\u201d Micronesia Seminar. http://micsem.org/pubs/ articles/alcodrug/alcfsm/frames/alcfsmfr.htm. Accessed 13 November 2010. Human Rights Council. 2010a. Draft Report of the Working Group on the Universal Periodic Review: Federated States of Micronesia. Geneva: United Nations General Assembly. .2010b. Summary Prepared by the Officer of the High Commissioner for Human Rights in accordance with paragraph 15 (c) of the annex to Human Rights Council resolution 5/1: Federated States of Micronesia. Geneva: United Nations General Assembly. Johnson, G. 2002. \u201cTeen Birth Rate High in Micronesia.\u201d http://www.fsmgov.org/press/ nw081202.htm. Accessed 31 October 2010. Magna Systems Incorporated. 2009. Needs Assessment of Youth Violence, Bullying, and Suicide in Pacific Islander Communities: Final Report. Los Angeles. Micronesia Bound. c. 2010. What is Micronesia Bound, Inc? Pohnpei. Information Booklet. National Department of Education. 2010. FSM National JEMCO 20 Education Indicators Report. Pohnpei. Office of the High Commissioner for Human Rights. 2008. \u201cBasic Facts about the UPR.\u201d http:// www.ohchr.org/EN/HRBodies/UPR/PAGES/BasicFacts.aspx. Accessed 14 November 2010. Pryor, J. 2007. Qualitative Adolescent Health & Development Study in Pohnpei and Chuuk States, Federated States of Micronesia. Suva: UNFPA. Rubinstein, DH. 2002. Youth Suicide and Social Change in Micronesia. Honolulu: Kagoshima University Research Center for the Pacific Islands. SBOC (Office of Statistics, Budget & Economic Management, Overseas Development Assistance & Compact Management). 2008. Statistical Yearbook: Federated States of Micronesia 2008. Pohnpei: National Government. U r b a n Y o U t h i n t h e P a c i f i c 51 .2007. Household Income and Expenditure Survey Analysis Report 2005. Pohnpei: National Government. .2001.", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "e90adebb-1b03-4468-b631-ebdc68b0e4ce": {"__data__": {"id_": "e90adebb-1b03-4468-b631-ebdc68b0e4ce", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/urban-youth-pacific-increasing-resilience-and-reducing-risk-involvement-crime-and-violence", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Urban Youth in the Pacific - Increasing Re